- fixed a possible issue with recreational drugs in inventory when "fulfilling outdoors" is triggered;
If you see pawns acting funny, don't mind to report your observations. "Hauling in between" and "hauling ALL before going to the crafting place" are two options that completely redo, how working on a bill works.
